email,role,barn_name,phone
# Closed-beta onboarding CSV — copy to beta-invites.csv (gitignored).
# SLH fills one row per trainer or owner in the 2026-05-25 launch batch.
#
# Columns:
#   email      (required) — recipient address; magic-link invite lands here.
#   role       (required) — 'owner' or 'trainer'. Trainers are auto-approved
#                           at claim time (admin.trainer.auto_approve audit).
#   barn_name  (optional) — stamped onto the invitation row; owner UI uses
#                           it as a default when the owner first loads /app.
#   phone      (optional) — for the on-call / PagerDuty-lite admin roster
#                           only. Not used for end-user SMS in closed beta.
#
# Rows beginning with '#' are treated as comments by scripts/import-beta-invites.mjs.
# Blank lines are ignored.
#
# Sample rows (delete before importing):
trainer1@example.com,trainer,,+15555550100
owner1@example.com,owner,"Windrose Stables",
